Name: View details invoice

Short Description: An employee views an invoices details.

Precondition: A invoice exists

Postcondition: The invoice details have been viewed.

Error Condition: No invoice exists

System state on error condition: No invoice details were viewed.

Actors: Employee

Trigger: Employee wishes to view invoice details.

Standard procedure:
(1) Employee wants to view invoice details.
(2) Employee searches for invoice.
(3) Employee views an invoices detail.

Alternate procedure:
(3') Employee is informed that no invoice exists. 
